{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876780/extras/sowhatNEW_RSZ.png?t=1582280991\" /><br>Kronorite is a nice little casual arcade game that you can hop into when you're bored and play with up to 10 people (5 vs 5). There are two teams which fight over the premise of having more terrain area than the other team. Each kill covers a portion of the other team's territory which gradually increases throughout the match.  <br>  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876780/extras/coremechanics_RSZ.png?t=1582280991\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> To counteract and protect yourself from getting killed, you put down crates. With time, you unlock different presets which help you build complex structures faster.<br></li><li> When getting killstreaks with the Archery class, you get arrow upgrades: splash damage arrows, lighting arrows and more!<br></li><li> On the other hand, with the tank class, you get other class specific power ups when your killstreak gets higher such as extra shields and speed. <br></li><li> Make great use of powerups to increase your chances of winning!<br></li><li> Each class has an important gameplay role which can change the flow of a match.</li></ul>  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876780/extras/environments_RSZ.png?t=1582280991\" /><br>Four different maps you can play on:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Aztec Jungle<br></li><li> Sakura Season<br></li><li> Frosty Winter<br></li><li> Antique Desert</li></ul>  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876780/extras/specialfeatures_RSZ.png?t=1582280991\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Parties: play with your friends!<br></li><li> Two game modes<br></li><li> Windows &amp; Linux cross-compatibility<br></li><li> Cosmetic items which you can 